---
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
numberOfLatestPostsToShow: 5
---
{% set postsCount = collections.posts | length %}
{% set latestPostsCount = postsCount | min(numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
{% set postslist = collections.posts | head(-1 * numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
{% set postslistCounter = postsCount %}
{% set morePosts = postsCount - numberOfLatestPostsToShow %}

<section class="showcase-hero">
	<div class="showcase-hero__content">
		<p class="showcase-eyebrow">Community AI Vibe</p>
		<h1 class="showcase-hero__title">Build With AI</h1>
		<p class="showcase-hero__lede">We’re a grassroots collective shipping open builds, sharing prompts, and remixing ideas across Malaysia and beyond.</p>
		<div class="showcase-hero__cta">
			<a class="showcase-button showcase-button--ghost" href="/blog/">Browse latest drops</a>
			<a class="showcase-button showcase-button--ghost" href="/about/">Learn about BWAI</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="showcase-hero__visual" aria-hidden="true">
		<div class="showcase-orbit">
			<div class="showcase-orbit__ring"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__ring"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__ring"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__node" style="top: 12%; left: 32%;" data-label="V0"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__node" style="bottom: 18%; right: 28%;" data-label="Lovable"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__node" style="top: 48%; right: 8%;" data-label="Bolt"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__core"><span>BWAI</span></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="showcase-section showcase-section--condensed">
	<header class="showcase-section__header">
		<p class="showcase-section__eyebrow">Beginner Tool</p>
		<h2 class="showcase-section__title">Optimised for beginner, build on browser, and Free trial</h2>
		<p class="showcase-section__lede">Dunno how to code? Fear not, you can turn your idea to working prototype in second with simple tool below.</p>
	</header>
	<div class="showcase-feature-grid">
		<article class="showcase-feature-card">
			<h3>Lovable</h3>
			<p>Build in backend and AI, focus on creative results, refine as you go.</p>
			<p class="showcase-feature-meta">friendly · beautiful UI</p>
		</article>
		<article class="showcase-feature-card">
			<h3>V0</h3>
			<p>Famous Vercel.app prompt driven builder. Super easy to deploy.</p>
			<p class="showcase-feature-meta">Budget · Developer</p>
		</article>
		<article class="showcase-feature-card">
			<h3>Bolt</h3>
			<p>Support deep integrations stripe, Figma, Supabase, workflow style development</p>
			<p class="showcase-feature-meta">Automation · Workflow</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="showcase-section">
	<header class="showcase-section__header">
		<p class="showcase-section__eyebrow">Latest drops</p>
		<h2 class="showcase-section__title">Project Showcase from BWAI community.</h2>
		<p class="showcase-section__lede">Catch the most recent {{ latestPostsCount }} release{% if latestPostsCount != 1 %}s{% endif %}, vibe-coded by the community.</p>
	</header>

	<div class="showcase-posts">
		{% include "postslist.njk" %}
		{% if morePosts > 0 %}
		<p class="showcase-more">{{ morePosts }} more post{% if morePosts != 1 %}s{% endif %} await in <a href="/blog/">the archive</a>.</p>
		{% endif %}
	</div>
</section>

